## Requirements

- Python >= 3.8
- pytorch_pretrained_bert >= 0.6.2
- langdetect >= 1.0.8
- numpy >= 1.21.3
- pandas >= 1.4.3
- lxml >= 4.6.2
- protobuf >= 3.14.0
- nltk >= 3.4.5

## How to install

### From PyPI

```text
pip install textcl
```

### From source/GitHub

```text
pip install git+https://github.com/alinapetukhova/textcl.git#egg=textcl
```

